body:
Because I assume it means, &quot;I have to play careful since anyone can kill me.&quot;

But I feel like people I talk to think it means, &quot;Only people with damage can kill me. Gotta be careful around them.&quot;

If being squishy didn&#039;t mean that anyone could kill you, then is it really being squishy?


